Stage 1 (GPU): extract features (4-pass forward → npz cache).
Stage 2 (CPU): compute scores from cache.
Stage 3 (CPU): pairwise accuracy per subset + global pooled + macro.
Stage 4 (CPU): aggregate all metrics into a single parquet for the issue body.
"""


